#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform2d.rst:17
msgid ""
"Represents one or many transformations in 2D space such as translation, "
"rotation, or scaling. It consists of two :ref:`x "
"<class_Transform2D_property_x>` and :ref:`y "
"<class_Transform2D_property_y>` :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>`\\ s and an"
" :ref:`origin <class_Transform2D_property_origin>`. It is similar to a "
"3×2 matrix."
msgstr ""
"表示2D空间中的一个或多个变换，例如平移、旋转或缩放。它由 :ref:`x "
"<class_Transform2D_property_x>`、:ref:`y <class_Transform2D_property_y>` "
"两个 :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` 和一个 :ref:`origin "
"<class_Transform2D_property_origin>` 组成。类似于3×2矩阵。"

