#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform2d.rst:80
msgid ""
"**IDENTITY** = **Transform2D( 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0 )** --- ``Transform2D`` "
"with no translation, rotation or scaling applied. When applied to other "
"data structures, :ref:`IDENTITY <class_Transform2D_constant_IDENTITY>` "
"performs no transformation."
msgstr ""
"**IDENTITY** = **Transform2D( 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0 )** —— 没有应用平移、旋转或缩放的 "
"``Transform2D``。 当应用于其他数据结构时，:ref:`IDENTITY "
"<class_Transform2D_constant_IDENTITY>` 不执行任何变换。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform2d.rst:82
msgid ""
"**FLIP_X** = **Transform2D( -1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0 )** --- ``Transform2D`` "
"with mirroring applied parallel to the X axis."
msgstr ""
"**FLIP_X** = **Transform2D( -1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0 )** —— 平行于X轴的应用镜像的 "
"``Transform2D``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform2d.rst:84
msgid ""
"**FLIP_Y** = **Transform2D( 1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0 )** --- ``Transform2D`` "
"with mirroring applied parallel to the Y axis."
msgstr ""
"**FLIP_Y** = **Transform2D( 1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0 )** —— 平行于Y轴应用镜像的 "
"``Transform2D``。"

